6q%3D90&cd=2023-03-20T04%3A12%3A47 624w,/_gatsby/image/3445c43d2fa38cf44473601212adebc9/a3099837545f3122089610391f67a378/how-to-manage-shop-by-brand-in-magento-2-2.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-manage-shop-by-brand-in-magento-2-2.png&a=w%3D1248%26h%3D528%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-20T04%3A12%3A47 1248w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 624px) 624px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":624,\"height\":264},\"alt\":\"\",\"className\":\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"3\"}</script></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 5: Add the Brand Navigation Block</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, you will need to add the brand navigation block to your store&#8217;s menu. This will allow customers to easily navigate to the brand page they are interested in. To add the brand navigation block, navigate to Content &gt; Blocks and click on the Add New Block button. Fill in the necessary information, such as the block title and identifier, and add the following code to the Content section:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>php\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"{{store url='brand/nike'}}\"&gt;Nike&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"{{store url='brand/adidas'}}\"&gt;Adidas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"{{store url='brand/puma'}}\"&gt;Puma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Replace nike, adidas, and puma with the brands you have assigned to your products.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To sum up, utilizing the &#8220;Shop by Brand&#8221; feature in Magento 2 can prove to be a valuable tool for product organization and enhancing the customer experience. Creating separate pages for each brand enables customers to conveniently browse and compare products from their preferred brands. With the use of attributes and categories, products can be filtered and organized, simplifying the search process for customers. By following the steps provided in this article, you can proficiently manage your shop by brand in Magento 2, resulting in a more streamlined and customer-friendly online store.</p>\n<div class='sfsi_Sicons sfsi_Sicons_position_left' style='float: none; vertical-align: middle; text-align:left'><div style='margin:0px 8px 0px 0px; line-height: 24px'><span>Please follow and like us:</span></div><div class='sfsi_socialwpr'><div class='sf_fb_share sf_icon' style='text-align:left;vertical-align: middle;'><a  target='_blank' rel='noopener' href='https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=/how-to-manage-shop-by-brand-in-magento-2/' style='display:inline-block;'><img class='sfsi_wicon'  data-pin-nopin='true' alt='fb-share-icon' title='Facebook Share' src='https://webguru.dev/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/share_icons/fb_icons/en_US.svg' /></a></div><div class='sf_twiter sf_icon' style='display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;margin-left: 7px;'>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a target='_blank' rel='noopener' href='https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=How+to+Manage+Shop+by+Brand+in+Magento+2+https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fhow-to-manage-shop-by-brand-in-magento-2%2F'style='display:inline-block' >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img data-pin-nopin= true class='sfsi_wicon' src='https://webguru.dev/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/share_icons/Twitter_Tweet/en_US_Tweet.svg' alt='Tweet' title='Tweet' >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" itemscope itemprop=\"author\"><div class=\"saboxplugin-tab\"><div class=\"saboxplugin-gravatar\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained  inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\"><div style=\"max-width:100px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentat